{"tid":632561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★瑞銀：iPhone中國銷量難回復2015年高峰","createTime":"2018-04-17T13:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T13:26:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"020669428b13a8e1424c44a027c1307b55735bc0","tid":632561,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"外媒報道引述瑞士銀行分析師米盧諾維奇（Steven Milunovich）發表報告稱，蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)在中國市場上的iPhone銷量今個財政年度，將無法回到2015年所觸及的高峰水平。<br />\n<br />\n米盧諾維奇預測，在蘋果公司今個財年中，其中國iPhone銷量增幅將大致持平，原因是消費者升級換代的時間周期變長，而且來自於中國本土智能手機廠商的競爭壓力正在加大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180417/bkn-20180417203139087-0417_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180417%2Fbkn-20180417203139087-0417_00842_001.html&d=SHWLV3NIdVJhD02CKTIBL7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f58a19a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180417/bkn-20180417203139087-0417_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6b93e13a69540b664641c7e23d16af5125a42e16","tid":632561,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7142ea00f739528a5d25cb9063b26e15eacd51d5","tid":632561,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"chi na use chi phone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}